    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/1d355ef561c2abe7a59cb6956bebbd72.avif?t=1753423573\" width=616 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你在不断为你的小公司招聘新人！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这还不够，你还得让所有人都能安置在自己的工作空间里。而且，他们不仅大小和形状各不相同，还有各种各样的要求！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 比如 乔治 ：他总是想坐在咖啡机旁边。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/02639bba68e86f7b7db89b8458bca91c.poster.avif?t=1753423573\" width=709 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/02639bba68e86f7b7db89b8458bca91c.webm?t=1753423573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有 格温和 格蕾丝，她们形影不离。可别想着把一个安排在房间这头，另一个丢到那头！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/f5b21bac9878262116eca0b6a6360500.poster.avif?t=1753423573\" width=708 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/f5b21bac9878262116eca0b6a6360500.webm?t=1753423573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/f5b21bac9878262116eca0b6a6360500.mp4?t=1753423573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总之，你懂的，《Cosy Company Puzzle》是一款需要深度思考的益智游戏！但最后，大家都会感觉舒服多了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>手工打造的关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90 个手工设计的关卡，其中有些将真正挑战你的脑力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单的操作</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需鼠标操作。左键拖动，右键旋转。没有任何东西会阻碍你的思维！  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>舒缓的 Lo-Fi 音乐</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充足的音乐资源将呵护你的耳朵，让你沉浸在轻松、适合思考的氛围中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>温馨友好的氛围</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职场通常意味着压力和效率，但在这里，我们放慢节奏，倾听每个人，并尊重每一位的独特之处。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可收集的卡牌</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事不仅通过谜题展开，还有 70 多张卡牌等你解锁与收集！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285260/extras/412aa85bd0073ee7e526ec26c3797853.avif?t=1753423573\" width=616 height=246 /></span></p>",
